cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper deals with the task of semantic segmentation using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of multimodal data and the proposed architecture and training procedure also involve aspects of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of digital surface models, which is a topic in graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO).
